node.text: Still feeling super tired and sick from the rona😷👎🏻 Spending most of my time just resting and trying to get better because I need to get back to fishing!🎣

node.text: Happy Friday y’all!☀️ I’m wishing I was fishing, but I’m hanging out on the couch trying to get better🤒 Y’all have a great weekend!🙌🏻
